262
00:18:56,520 --> 00:19:01,240
He's very caring and considerate.

263
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,880
<i>We have very busy schedules,</i>

264
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:06,120
<i>but we do our best
to make time for each other.</i>

265
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:09,320
<i>Have you thought about
clearing out some time</i>

266
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:11,880
<i>to plan your wedding</i>

267
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,160
<i>or prepare for a honeymoon?</i>

268
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:16,640
<i>At present, I'm focusing on my career.</i>

269
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:20,080
<i>I haven't thought about the wedding yet.</i>

270
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:23,040
<i>You're in your prime right now.</i>

271
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:24,680
<i>Do you have any other plans?</i>

272
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:28,600
<i>I will work hard to show you
more of my acting talents.</i>

273
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:30,920
<i>I hope all of you will continue
to support me.</i>

274
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:32,480
<i>That's all for today's program.</i>

275
00:19:32,560 --> 00:19:33,480
Until next week!

276
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:36,000
See you next time!

277
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:39,840
That was a success. Thank you, Luo.

278
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,520
Not at all. It was my pleasure.

279
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:42,560
We'll be leaving now.

280
00:19:44,280 --> 00:19:45,160
Let's go.

281
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,440
That was great.

282
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:50,120
Did you pay people
to write supportive comments?

283
00:19:50,280 --> 00:19:52,240
As if I would pay such dumb supporters.

284
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:54,000
Do you think your rival did it?

285
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:57,360
What kind of rival would spend
a hundred thousand on gifts

286
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,480
just to prank me?

287
00:19:58,560 --> 00:19:59,720
That's foolish.

288
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:03,160
Your popularity has soared
because of your engagement.

289
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:07,560
I was contacted by a variety show,
<i>Romantic Departure</i>, a few days ago.

290
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:09,440
They invite you and Ling Yizhou
to join the show

291
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:11,960
to film your daily life as a couple.

292
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:15,400
I did some searching online.
The show is quite popular.

293
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:18,840
Going on the show
will help your reputation and image.

294
00:20:19,720 --> 00:20:22,200
Ms. Jiang, you know Ling Yizhou and I...

295
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:24,560
aren't a real-life couple.

296
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:25,920
We don't get along.

297
00:20:26,280 --> 00:20:28,520
We'll be exposed if we go to the show.

298
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:31,120
Besides, I don't want to mix
my personal life and work.

299
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:34,240
When did Ling Yizhou
become a part of your life?

300
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,840
You don't have any acting jobs.

301
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:38,320
You desperately need the exposure.

302
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:40,440
This variety show
is an excellent opportunity.

303
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:44,560
Even if I agree to it,
Ling Yizhou wouldn't.

304
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,160
Not necessarily.

305
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:49,040
It was his idea to get engaged.

306
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,880
So many people are saying
it's just an act.

307
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:53,320
If such opinions continue to brew,

308
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:55,840
it would be detrimental
for him and Lingshi Group.

309
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:57,800
Look at me.

310
00:20:58,240 --> 00:21:00,920
Besides, I already accepted the offer.

311
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:04,080
We'll have to pay a hefty sum
if we break the contract.

312
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,080
I...

313
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,800
I can't afford it.

314
00:21:08,320 --> 00:21:09,400
What?

315
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:16,080
Chu Yan, let's get going.

316
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:17,360
The director is getting impatient.

317
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:20,480
Right. Is your phone getting a signal?

318
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:22,840
No.

319
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:26,960
Just bear with it for another two days.

320
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:28,760
We'll be heading back then.

321
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,320
-All right.
-Let's go.

322
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,000
<i>-This way, please.
-Okay.</i>

323
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:37,040
LINGSHI GROUP

324
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:40,000
Mr. Ling is in a meeting.
He will be here shortly.

325
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,440
Okay, we'll wait here.

326
00:21:42,520 --> 00:21:44,080
How about some coffee?

327
00:21:44,280 --> 00:21:46,080
-Yes, thank you.
-Thank you.

328
00:21:50,840 --> 00:21:54,160
This is my first time
in a chairman's office.

329
00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:57,640
It's not that impressive.

330
00:21:57,720 --> 00:22:00,000
The ones in my scripts are more luxurious.

331
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:01,280
What do you know?

332
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:02,680
He likes to maintain a low profile.

333
00:22:02,760 --> 00:22:04,840
Besides, there aren't that many tycoons.

334
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:09,560
Mrs. Ling, you adjusted to your role
quite quickly.

335
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:11,720
You're hitting me
while I'm down, aren't you?

336
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:17,480
Sorry, I was held up.

337
00:22:17,560 --> 00:22:19,360
-Thank you for waiting.
-It's okay.

338
00:22:20,040 --> 00:22:22,240
This is my friend, Jia Fei.

339
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,000
Hello, Ms. Jia.

340
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,440
Be careful.

341
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:05,680
Ms. Jia?

342
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:09,880
Linlin,

343
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:14,360
I suddenly remembered
I haven't finished my work yet.

344
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,440
I need to go.

345
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:17,600
Take your time talking. Bye.

346
00:23:17,680 --> 00:23:19,360
Wen Li can drive you if you're in a hurry.

347
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:20,800
No, thank you.

348
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:29,200
She's probably busy writing
for a new drama.

349
00:23:30,040 --> 00:23:31,000
Wen Li, give her a ride.

350
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,200
-Sit, Mumu.
-Okay.

351
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:48,000
Ms. Jia, I'll see you down.

352
00:23:48,080 --> 00:23:49,480
No, thank you.

353
00:23:49,560 --> 00:23:50,720
Was it you at the fencing club?

354
00:23:51,120 --> 00:23:51,960
It wasn't me!

355
00:23:52,040 --> 00:23:53,240
Was it you at the bar?

356
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:55,480
Like I said, it wasn't me!

357
00:23:56,320 --> 00:23:57,240
It wasn't?

358
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:58,440
That can't be.

359
00:24:00,080 --> 00:24:01,480
The ring!

360
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:11,640
My manager accepted a variety show for me.

361
00:24:11,960 --> 00:24:15,200
I didn't want to bother you.

362
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:17,680
But due to the unusual circumstances,

363
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:21,280
I hope you'll take part
in the show with me.

364
00:24:21,360 --> 00:24:22,920
<i>ROMANTIC DEPARTURE</i> PROPOSAL

365
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:25,840
There's a reason you need to participate,

366
00:24:26,080 --> 00:24:27,280
but I don't, right?

367
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:30,880
Everybody knows we're engaged now.

368
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:35,240
But because it happened so suddenly,
there are a lot of doubts.

369
00:24:35,600 --> 00:24:37,200
It's also stated in our contract.

370
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:39,000
"We need to increase our exposure

371
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:41,600
to prove the authenticity
of our relationship."

372
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:44,560
This is the best way to do so.

373
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,040
One more thing.

374
00:24:46,240 --> 00:24:48,480
I had a live interview recently

375
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:50,600
and there were a bunch of paid supporters

376
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:53,080
who submitted idiotic and fake comments.

377
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:57,520
That has led to even more people
having suspicions about our relationship.

378
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:03,200
So we desperately need this show
to deceive...

379
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:07,000
I mean, to suppress such suspicions.

380
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,080
I'll do it.

381
00:25:16,560 --> 00:25:17,480
Hello, Wen Li?

382
00:25:17,840 --> 00:25:19,240
Contact Cheng Li.

383
00:25:19,440 --> 00:25:21,520
Push my meeting with him next week.

384
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:22,880
Yes.

385
00:25:23,120 --> 00:25:26,320
Also, please tell him
I've reviewed his proposal and I like it.

386
00:25:26,880 --> 00:25:28,320
Okay. That's all.

387
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:31,960
I'm sorry.

388
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:36,880
I won't trouble you
with this sort of thing again.

389
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:38,800
It won't happen again.

390
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,640
Why are you sorry?

391
00:25:41,280 --> 00:25:42,840
I would never accept an unprofitable deal.

392
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:47,200
True to your businessman nature.

393
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:49,600
So what conditions do you have?

394
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:52,560
If I'm going to be on the show,

395
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:55,080
we can't make any mistakes
in front of the film crew.

396
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:58,200
I want to rehearse beforehand.

397
00:25:59,320 --> 00:26:01,320
You're quite dedicated to the act.

398
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:04,880
Starting tomorrow,
come to my house for rehearsals.

399
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,200
What's this?

400
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:28,880
I had Wen Li write up
the story of how we met.

401
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:31,560
We need to get our stories straight
in case anyone asks.

402
00:26:32,600 --> 00:26:34,960
Mr. Wen sure is skilled at everything.

403
00:26:40,800 --> 00:26:42,840
"The event was about to start

404
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:46,480
<i>and Xia Lin was rushing to the venue.</i>

405
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:07,200
Since then,
the two have been inseparable."

406
00:27:08,840 --> 00:27:11,040
This is so corny!

407
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:14,720
How is it compared to the real story?

408
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:18,320
At least the actual experience
didn't defy any laws of physics.

409
00:27:18,960 --> 00:27:20,120
We embraced and spun in circles.

410
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:21,560
Were we waltzing?

411
00:27:21,840 --> 00:27:25,000
If we were kissing like that,
we would have chipped our front teeth.

412
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:28,920
How should we have kissed?

413
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:33,840
At least like...

414
00:27:37,840 --> 00:27:39,320
Why are we discussing this?

415
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:43,680
I just mean that the more we reveal,
the more likely we'll slip up.

416
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:47,640
We're better off saying
we met at an event.

417
00:27:47,760 --> 00:27:50,440
You were mesmerized by my beauty,

418
00:27:50,800 --> 00:27:54,240
fell hopelessly in love with me
at first sight

419
00:27:54,320 --> 00:27:56,280
and wouldn't take no for an answer.

420
00:27:56,440 --> 00:28:00,840
I had no choice but to accept you.

421
00:28:01,600 --> 00:28:03,880
-Sure, let's go with that.
-It's just nonsense.

422
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:05,280
No, I think it's great.

423
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:08,240
Hungry?

424
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:14,080
Are you going to cook?

425
00:28:14,600 --> 00:28:16,440
Don't you want to try my cooking?

426
00:28:16,560 --> 00:28:18,160
I don't want to trouble you.

427
00:28:20,600 --> 00:28:23,280
All right. I'll explore your place.

428
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:36,520
<i>Romantic Departure</i> announced
their guest lineups today.

429
00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:37,960
Who's included?

430
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:41,000
Niko, Wang Peng, Xia Lin, and Ling Yizhou.

431
00:28:42,320 --> 00:28:43,280
Which Xia Lin?

432
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,800
The one you know.

433
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:48,680
Xia Lin got onto a reality show?

434
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:53,560
A reality dating show?

435
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:55,920
Yes. They are engaged, right?

436
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:58,040
They will be showing off
how sweet they are.

437
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:00,600
Engaged?

438
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:02,600
They announced it a few days ago.

439
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,800
You were away filming at the time.

440
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:10,120
How can they be engaged?

441
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:12,000
It must be fake.

442
00:29:12,360 --> 00:29:13,480
It can't be true.

443
00:29:25,120 --> 00:29:26,320
Hello, Chu Yan.

444
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:27,720
<i>Did you wrap up filming?</i>

445
00:29:27,800 --> 00:29:29,080
What did Ling Yizhou do to you?

446
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:36,400
Are you and Ling Yizhou engaged?

447
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:37,880
You just found out?

448
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:40,040
I thought you already saw the news.

449
00:29:40,800 --> 00:29:41,640
Well, I'm sorry.

450
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:43,920
I must be the last person on Earth
to find out.

451
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:47,640
What's going on
between you and Ling Yizhou?

452
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:49,880
You didn't know him at the charity gala.

453
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:52,480
I knew him.

454
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:54,920
I was just messing with you.

455
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:58,720
Really? Then why didn't you
tell me about him?

456
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,600
<i>We agreed to keep it a secret.</i>

457
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:03,360
Not even my manager knew about it.

458
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:07,080
Didn't you say
you wanted to focus on your career?

459
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,720
Why the sudden change of heart?

460
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:12,200
That's how life is.

461
00:30:12,280 --> 00:30:13,960
It's full of surprises.

462
00:30:14,280 --> 00:30:15,680
Mumu, come give me a hand.

463
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,040
Okay, I'm coming.

464
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:19,960
Are you with Ling Yizhou?

465
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:21,760
I'm at his house.

466
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,280
Who's on the phone?

467
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,400
<i>Chu Yan.</i>

468
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:27,080
Put him on the phone.

469
00:30:28,080 --> 00:30:29,440
He wants to talk to you.

470
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:32,960
Hello?

471
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:38,560
Childish.

472
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:40,680
Did he hang up?

473
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:49,560
What did Chu Yan say?

474
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:50,760
He told me

475
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:52,800
your cooking is delicious.

476
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,480
He's lying.

477
00:30:55,120 --> 00:30:58,080
I don't think
I'll be very helpful in the kitchen.

478
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,400
-I should get out--
-You can help.

479
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,800
Can you wash these for me?

480
00:31:05,120 --> 00:31:06,080
Okay.

481
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,520
He's still acting like
a three-year-old child.

482
00:31:11,840 --> 00:31:13,640
How long have you known each other?

483
00:31:14,120 --> 00:31:15,720
Unfortunately,
since we were three years old.

484
00:31:40,520 --> 00:31:41,600
Ling Yizhou.

485
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:45,160
Have you ever watched the film <i>Zorro</i>?

486
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:47,920
Why?

487
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:53,400
Did you attend a masquerade two years ago?

488
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:57,200
Did you wear a gold and silver mask

489
00:31:57,600 --> 00:32:00,000
with a lipstick print on its right side?

490
00:32:01,600 --> 00:32:02,640
Do you wish that I was there?

491
00:32:02,760 --> 00:32:04,840
Just tell me yes or no.

492
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:08,400
I usually don't go to such events.

493
00:32:13,840 --> 00:32:16,320
By the way, I have to remind you.

494
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:19,600
Even though we are
only in a contract relationship,

495
00:32:20,080 --> 00:32:22,920
I would like for us
to be faithful to each other

496
00:32:23,360 --> 00:32:27,600
during the contract period, my dear wife.

497
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:53,880
I can do it myself.

498
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:55,160
I can do it.

499
00:33:09,840 --> 00:33:10,720
All done.

500
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:17,080
Is there anything else you need help with?

501
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,000
Wash the vegetables.

502
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:20,160
That's right. Wash them.

503
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:34,240
You cut your finger! You're bleeding!

504
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:36,280
Open your mouth! Right now!

505
00:33:37,560 --> 00:33:38,960
Suck on it to disinfect it.

506
00:33:39,040 --> 00:33:40,560
Wait here. I'll go get a bandage.

507
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:45,199
Goodness.

508
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:48,600
One, two, and three.

509
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:51,000
It's terrifying
how many cameras there are.

510
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:54,120
There's even one here.
Is getting a drink worth filming?

511
00:34:54,239 --> 00:34:56,960
It's necessary for capturing
the desired footage for the show.

512
00:34:58,600 --> 00:35:01,040
Following the rules for the film crew,

513
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:03,000
we'll hold on to your luggage
for the time being.

514
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:05,880
We'll be providing you
with daily essentials later.

515
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,560
Don't worry. We will cooperate with you.

516
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:10,680
Are we receiving a mission or something?

517
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:12,240
Isn't that how these shows usually go?

518
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:17,200
-A dog?
-A dog?

519
00:35:18,560 --> 00:35:19,760
It's so cute!

520
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:24,400
What a cutie. What's your name?

521
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:27,800
This dog will be in your care
during the three days that you're here.

522
00:35:27,880 --> 00:35:28,760
Really?

523
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,840
That's awesome.
Ling Yizhou, let's give it a name.

524
00:35:32,520 --> 00:35:33,480
Take it away.

